{"about_the_game":"Dive into the universe of <strong>Chaos Crafters</strong>, where the art of magic is at your fingertips! As an apprentice wizard, you'll explore the corners of this school in search of ingredients to craft your own spells. Each spell is unique, powerful, and essential for overcoming the challenges that the Academy presents.<br><br>You'll use your magic to solve complex puzzles and to fight formidable enemies, all while developing your own style of sorcery. But the power of spells isn't limited to problem-solving and combat: it's also a source of fun and surprising interactions!<br><br>At Chaos Crafters Academy, your friends can quickly become your favorite guinea pigs. Make them inflate until they float like balloons, transform them into mischievous animals, or reduce their size to make them fit through tight spaces. Even the creatures of the Academy aren't safe from your enchantments.<br><br>In this multifaceted game, each corridor of the academy can become a playground for your magical experiments. Get ready for an epic adventure where spell crafting, combat, puzzles, and playful interactions intertwine. Wands ready, let your spells fly! Chaos Crafters awaits you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524650/extras/Follow.gif?t=1720430744\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524650/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1720430744","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524650/page.bg.jpg?t=1720430744","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524650/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1720430744","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524650/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1720430744","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-o